frames.caption: A herd of reindeer runs through a snowy forest under the vibrant display of the Northern Lights. The scene captures the natural beauty of the aurora borealis illuminating the night sky, with snow-laden trees lining the path. The reindeer, with their majestic antlers, create a sense of movement and vitality in the serene winter landscape.
